Invocation Name: summer gardening tip
des:
Ask for summer gardening tips, and learn how to better protect your garden.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Summer Gardening Tip" or "Alexa, open Summer Gardening Tip" to get a tip".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop" or "Alexa goodbye"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
